OL,3,CDrug poisoning deaths in England and
OL,4,CWales at record high
OL,6,FDrug poisoning deaths in England and
OL,7,FWales have risen for the 11th
OL,8,Fconsecutive year, to the highest
OL,9,Fnumber since records began in 1993.
OL,11,FData from the Office for National
OL,12,FStatistics (ONS) found there were
OL,13,F5,448 deaths related to drug poisoning
OL,14,Fregistered in England and Wales in
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FIt also showed nearly half of those
OL,18,Finvolved an opiate 2,551 deaths, while
OL,19,F1,118 deaths involved cocaine, which
OL,20,Fis 30.5% more than 2022.
