OL,3,CDrug poisoning deaths in England and
OL,4,CWales at record high
OL,6,FThere is an overall increase in drug
OL,7,Fpoisoning deaths from from 2022, when
OL,8,Fthere were 4,907 deaths. The death
OL,9,Frate has risen every year since 2012,
OL,10,Fafter remaining relatively stable over
OL,11,Fthe preceding two decades.
OL,13,FData showed that of drug-poisoning
OL,14,Fdeaths registered, the main cause was
OL,15,Fidentified as drug misuse, with rates
OL,16,Fof drug misuse deaths continue to be
OL,17,Felevated among those born in the
OL,18,F1970s, often referred to as
OL,19,F"Generation X", with the highest rate
OL,20,Fin those aged 40 to 49 years.
