OL,6,FOf those, the North East continues to
OL,7,Fhave the highest rates of deaths
OL,8,Frelating to drug poisoning and drug
OL,9,Fmisuse (174.3 deaths per million
OL,10,Fpeople and 108.5 per million,
OL,11,Frespectively), while London had the
OL,12,Flowest rate for drug poisoning and
OL,13,Fdrug misuse (58.1 deaths per million
OL,14,Fpeople and 41.0 per million,
OL,15,Frespectively).
