OL,3,CDrug poisoning deaths in England and
OL,4,CWales at record high
OL,6,FIn Wales, 377 deaths related to drug
OL,7,Fpoisoning were registered in 2023, the
OL,8,Fequivalent of 129.2 deaths per million
OL,9,Fpeople. This is higher than the rate
OL,10,Frecorded in 2022 (109.6 deaths per
OL,11,Fmillion, 318 deaths).
OL,13,FCraig Whitelock manages Community
OL,14,FLinks in Hartlepool, a support group
OL,15,Ffor people struggling with addiction
OL,16,Fand substance misuse. Craig, a former
OL,17,Faddict himself, set the group up last
OL,18,Fyear in response to the growing need
OL,19,Ffor support services in the area.
