OL,6,F"Drugs are ripping the community to
OL,7,Fbits," he told ITV News. "Some weeks
OL,8,Fwe get 50 people in, some weeks we get
OL,9,F60."
OL,11,F"Crack cocaine unfortunately is the
OL,12,Fnew cannabis," Craig said
OL,14,FIn the last 18 months, Community Links
OL,15,Fhas helped over 70 people through
OL,16,Faddiction but the group warned that
OL,17,Fthe problem is getting bigger, with
OL,18,Fpeople being able to get drugs in
OL,19,FHartlepool quicker than a takeaway
OL,20,Fpizza.
