OL,3,CDrug poisoning deaths in England and
OL,4,CWales at record high
OL,6,FHannah Newbyy came to Community Links
OL,7,Fin February after becoming addicted to
OL,8,Fcrack cocaine.
OL,10,F"Once I tried it, I was hooked, it's
OL,11,Fthe devil, it takes your soul," she
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FShe said the addiction took everything
OL,15,Ffrom her, including her job, her home
OL,16,Fand her children.
OL,18,FShe told ITV News that she spent up to
OL,19,F#1,500 a month on drugs and sold the
OL,20,Fcontents of her house to be able to
OL,21,Fafford it.
